'''Pocket Jeunesse''' is the children's book imprint of the [[Univers Poche]] [[wikipedia:France|French]] publishing company. Founded in [[1940s|1944]], Pocket Jeunesse is responsible for printing the [[wikipedia:French language|French]] translations of the ''[[Star Wars]]'' young reader novels.

